<div class="title">Don't Mix These</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I, Lithium, Cannabis & Alprazolam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=2C-I&Exact=1">2C-I</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; 2C-I. "Don't Mix These: An Experience with 2C-I, Lithium, Cannabis & Alprazolam (exp39730)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 5, 2005. erowid.org/exp/39730</div>

<br/>



